Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢搭乘
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↓Title↓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:55.86,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(425,275)}{\fad(0,500)}槛发
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↑Title↑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}各位观众午安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:02:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}现在是TVS午间新闻时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}今天要变更预定节目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  真是吓我一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}报导连续变态杀人的后继消息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到我们昨天待的地方竟然正在发生命案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是那时候犯人正在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  真是太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是找到犯人我就可以狠狠揍扁他了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶她没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一个人先跑回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天起就有点怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}被害人是住在神奈川县的某公司员工  安藤智美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}当天晚上七点左右因为心情不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}就跟一起来的朋友分开一个人坐上摩天轮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐  你知不知道是什么原因？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:02:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚刚开始就一直发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来不像是没事的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭也没好好吃对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是没有食欲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哪里觉得不舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从去游乐园那天开始就觉得你不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是身体不太舒服而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Ciel学姐之间发生了什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事也没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我一个人静一静
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一下  秋叶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶  振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶  秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不请医生来看真的没关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要休息一阵子就会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶小姐不也是那么说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  不要去找医生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:05:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果叫医生来的话我会恨哥哥一辈子的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的身体自己最清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会复原的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你之前明明还很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是精神上的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神上的原因？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶小姐只要情绪一不稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵先生回来之后状况比以前好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我让她担心这担心那的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上不会出去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您一定要待在秋叶小姐身边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最好的药了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了一个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得了感冒那一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张开眼睛就看到哥哥在旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬间  感觉好像回到那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多休息一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我会陪在你旁边的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间快到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐一定要吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天也要好好躺着休息喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一直在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  因为秋叶不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边的状况怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说没有收获
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很抱歉不过  暂时没办法陪你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来就算我被Roa干掉  志贵也不在乎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没那么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明对我那么冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…发生了一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以陪我喝杯茶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病倒在床上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么果然没错？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我就一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐你是一个什么样的人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟远野你知道的一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  远野你对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是谁都有秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野  你不是也有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢跟远野你们几个在一起度过的快乐时光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是可以的话  我想一直这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请再让我多当一阵子爱管闲事的学姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:12:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么时候我都会站在远野这一边喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句话是什么意思呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵少爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:13:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  已经完全好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏有哥哥陪在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想问你傍晚的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候  我出去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见你在秋叶的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是不是做梦了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可以出来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹康复了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问个奇怪的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找的那家伙是男的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指Roa？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能这样断定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然原本的Roa是男的不过  宿主都有共通点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么共通点？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都是特殊的家族的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊的家族？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如混有“非人者”的血液之类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在槙久老爷的房间有何贵干？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不知不觉感到很怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前觉得老爸的书房难以亲近根本没想过要来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我们这个家族还真不平常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这句话是什么意思呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但大家都很早过世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还没有一个是正常死亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不会有点异常吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿洗好的衣服过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它还有什么吩咐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是不是对我隐瞒了什么事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐瞒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家的事、秋叶的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我遗忘的往事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如混有“非人者”的血液之类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候出现的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那个样子来判断大概是一个小时前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有他的气息吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是宿主的人格太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还待在家里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍  稍微有点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么知道这件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然她的确不是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你和你妹妹吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看得见？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口很痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起那个伤口的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.90,0:21:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.70,0:22:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
